  "description": "<i>Advanced Soccer Simulator</i> is a football/soccer management game for up to eight players.  You choose from one of 80 teams from England and Scotland which are split into four divisions consisting of 20 teams each.  Each team has a squad of up to 16 players.  You begin in Division 4 and your aim is to finish in the top 3 and earn promotion.<br><br>A season consists of 38 league matches plus matches in the League Cup and F.A. Cup.  You can make adjustments to your playing squad and even buy or sell players in the transfer market.  Each match is presented with highlights which shows all the scoring chances of the game.",
